        android:text="Love Café opened in 14th February of 2011 by two enthusiastic young men as a cozy cafe hidden within Project-shop clothing store. This seven years old charming and understated spot quickly gained many fans for its hearty takes on savory cafe classics, famous truffle shoestring fries and indulgent cakes, burgers and pastas. Thoughtfully detailed interiors, lush surroundings, friendly relaxed service and generous portions have made this homegrown Singapore brand an internationally recognized local favorite. Love Café is the place for extraordinary brunches, lazy afternoon teas, romantic dates and friendly celebrations in beautiful surroundings."
